Storyline:
Dusty Crophopper is a little cropduster plane with a fear of heights and a crazy
dream of being a racer. While his friends need convincing, Dusty gets the
training he needs from Skipper, a veteran fighter, and qualifies for the Wings
Across the World race. In the event, Dusty finds competitors who soon learn that
there is something special about this underdog as he is tested to his physical
and emotional limits. In doing so, Dusty soon finds enemies, and more
importantly friends, who are inspired by his dream. In the face of all
obstacles, the winner of this air race will be anyone's guess.
